{"data":[{"id":560466197,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b8dcf43f4aea99122fc1c1b5311ee806","url_token":"dao-xie-ban-hu-ming-yue","name":"倒泻半湖明月","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0912a602ae409f778f30ca3ece8013e6_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0912a602ae409f778f30ca3ece8013e6_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b8dcf43f4aea99122fc1c1b5311ee806","user_type":"people","headline":"理工科大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":70,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560466197","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1937ffcd798abe9541d75ef1e4ec55c5_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839978,"updated_time":1546315409,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1268,"comment_count":200,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"新年快乐。\u003cbr\u003e证明先生删帖了。全删了。\u003cbr\u003e哈哈哈哈没想到吧我还有。\u003cbr\u003e来来来挂上。\u003cbr\u003e权且博诸君一乐。\u003cbr\u003e新年嘛，当然要从快乐开始了。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e第一部分:思路:有借有还，再借不难。\u003cbr\u003e分类讨论，逐一判断。\u003cbr\u003e准备:1.设集合A为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e2.设集合B为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数只包括正质数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e3.任意大于等于4的偶数均可以表示为(6k- 2),6k,(6k+2)中的一种。其中k为正整数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e目的:证明任意n∈正整数且n\u0026gt; = 2时，2n∈B是真命题。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1937ffcd798abe9541d75ef1e4ec55c5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" w